{
  "texts": [
    "The conversion is possible between different types of representations, e.g.",
    "from discrete points to meshes, however, the conversion time is often a bottleneck in the processing pipeline.",
    "The largest impact for the 3D domain had the work of Kingma and Welling (2014).",
    "Based on the input data specific categories, the most impact for the discrete point cloud processing has Gadelha et al. (2018), while for voxel grid representation of 3D space Brock et al. (2016) and Tan et al. (2018) for the deforming meshes.",
    "These different data types were the first level for our taxonomy, while the various applications represent the further levels of taxonomy."
  ]
}